[[Duke Grigor Verdige]] the last Duke of [[Calhun]] dissapeard with [[Dorringrad]] at the end of [[the war|The Fall]], but his palace still stands. Backing onto the cliffs of [[Lyrin Bay]], this stately home has long since been picked clean by scavangers, and is now home to many squatters. Those that live there are those at the very bottom of society. Substance abuse and crime is rampant in the palace, as it's inhabitants struggle to survive.